1
00:00:01,280 --> 00:00:02,240
What's up, my daughter?

2
00:00:06,760 --> 00:00:09,020
I can feel your sadness from far away.

3
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:17,640
Did you fight with Valentina?

4
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:21,120
Not at all.

5
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:24,700
What is it then?

6
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:35,280
Juli, I know that...

7
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:41,480
you're grown up, you have the right to have your private life and keep secrets,

8
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:50,560
but I want you to know that I am here to protect you,

9
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,720
to take care of you,

10
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:57,280
to listen to you.

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,460
You can trust me.

12
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:11,440
Sometimes, secrets can suffocate you.

13
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,260
Believe me, I would know.

14
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:18,780
Mom.

15
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,960
I want to sleep.

16
00:01:36,255 --> 00:01:37,255
Alright.

17
00:01:43,885 --> 00:00:00,000
Rest well.

